**Markdown shape.** Matches GOOG.md lines 148–158 and ASML.md lines 162–172 as-written (each bullet ends with `[interface layer]`, `[demand layer]`, etc.). Zero markdown changes.

**Layer palette (fixed across all playbooks).** The renderer maps each layer literal to a token pair; the table below is the authoritative mapping and must be reproduced verbatim in the catalogue entry:

| Layer literal | Class | Background token | Foreground token |
|---|---|---|---|
| `interface` | `p-fm-tag-interface` | `--accent-soft` | `--accent` |
| `monetisation` / `monetization` | `p-fm-tag-monetisation` | `--info-soft` | `--info` |
| `cost` | `p-fm-tag-cost` | `--warn-soft` | `--warn` |
