<div class="p-axis-card">
  <div class="p-axis-head">
    <h3 id="axis-1">1. Capex-cycle trough timing</h3>
    <p class="p-axis-q">Does the capex cycle trough in H2 2026…</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-axis-body">
